{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1738256219\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nif Nif is a wholesome deckbuilder about helping the forest and your animal pals, designed to be easy to pick up for beginners of the genre, but with strategic depth for those who want a challenge! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build the best deck!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your cards with special abilities as you progress through the levels to be best prepared to face the final bosses that await you at the end of the forest. Decide what to bring on each adventure to keep things fresh, and choose between two characters, each with unique cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/extras/clean.gif?t=1738256219\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can collect seeds, plant them and cook your own power-up potions in the form of delicious hot soups!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/extras/soup.gif?t=1738256219\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wholesome and chill </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nif Nif is a comfortable and cozy experience set in a whimsical colorful world full of friendly and quirky characters that our little piglet will meet along the way on lovely encounters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/extras/chill.gif?t=1738256219\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">For EVERYONE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed for a general audience: from fans of deck-builders or cozy games, to kids (it helps them practice mental math!) or even people with no experience in video games. Accessible and totally non-violent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/extras/storyevent.gif?t=1738256219\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Includes\u2026</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Procedurally generated maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two playable characters (Nif Nif and Cat) with different decks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gardening and cooking mini game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlockable hats to change abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Progress through levels, unlockables and achievements</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738256219","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/page.bg.jpg?t=1738256219","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738256219","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738256219","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2631650/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1738256219\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nif Nif is a wholesome deckbuilder about helping the forest and your animal pals, designed to be easy to pick up for beginners of the genre, but with strategic depth for those who want a challenge! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build the best deck!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your cards with special abilities as you progress through the